data.description: Welcome to this adorable home that offers peaceful country living but is conveniently located to all the modern conveniences in Hardin County. You can enjoy the sun rise on the large front porch and watch the sun set on the private deck on the back of this home. This 3 bedroom / 2 full bath house offers the popular open floor plan that so many home buyers desire. The partially finished basement has a spacious second living area with the second bathroom. You will also find a large utility room with loads of storage space in the basement. This home truly is spectacular and is nestled on just under an acre with the perfect blend of cleared and wooded land. The HVAC is new in 2023. There is a transferable home warranty in place.
